#. module: pet_groomer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pet_groomer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Point of Sale allows grooming salons to complete transactions quickly and efficiently at the counter. It is designed\n"
"            for fast service, enabling staff to charge grooming sessions and retail products in a single flow while supporting\n"
"            multiple payment methods."
msgstr ""
"Het kassasysteem kan trimsalons helpen transacties snel en efficiënt af te "
